title: SonicWall: CPU Utilization
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/sonicwall
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the CPU utilization of SonicWall firewalls in percent.

 The levels for the utilization in percent can be configured via the rule
 "SonicWall CPU utilization". Default levels are 80%/95%.

 The check uses the SONICWALL-FIREWALL-IP-STATISTICS-MIB.

discovery:
 One service is created per host.
